---
title: Smart Honey-Garlic Turkey Meatballs with Cheesy Broccoli and Cauliflower-Potato Mash
description: We've slashed the starch in half in this cal and carb smart supper! In place of some of the potatoes, we've added wholesome cauliflower to the mash.

Smart is based on a per serving calculation of the recipe's kilocalorie and carbohydrate amount.
